    @Deprecated
public interface DirectedGraph<V,E>
extends Graph<V,E>
    A graph whose all edges are directed. This is the root interface of all directed graphs.

    See http://mathworld.wolfram.com/DirectedGraph.html for more on directed graphs.

    Since:
    Jul 14, 2003
    Author:
    Barak Naveh
